## Architecture

This package follows the NetScript plugin package archetype.

The manifest is the public contract.

The CLI is a thin command adapter.

The Aspire contribution is a composition adapter.

The e2e gates are verification adapters.

Testing fixtures are isolated from runtime code.

Generated code is not committed by the plugin package.

